<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- {فَمَنْ شَهِدَ <span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span> مِنْكُمُ الشَّهْرَ فَلْيَصُمْهُ} <span style="color:#008000">(٤)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- <span style="color:#947721">{شَهْرُ رَمَضَانَ الَّذِي أُنْزِلَ فِيهِ الْقُرْآنُ هُدًى لِلنَّاسِ وَبَيِّنَاتٍ مِنَ الْهُدَى وَالْفُرْقَانِ}</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٥)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
